含まれているクラス:
Magic
public static class Magic.ForbiddenMagic extends Object
This class provides methods that may be specific to a runtime. Their existence and behavior is not guaranteed across future versions. They may be poorly named, throw exception, have misleading parameters, or any other bad programming practice. Programmers should not rely on these methods, as they may be removed at anytime in the future. Use with caution!

Remember: This is forbidden magic, don't expect methods to work.

    • getPrimitiveClass

      @NotNull public @NotNull Class<?> getPrimitiveClass(@NotNull @NotNull String type) throws ClassNotFoundException, NullPointerException
      Return the Virtual Machine's Class object for the named primitive type. The result class is equivalent to <BoxedPrimitiveType>.TYPE.

      Remember: This is forbidden magic.

      戻り値:
      primitive class
      例外:
      ClassNotFoundException - when class was not found by specified type.
      NullPointerException - when null was provided to the type.

    • getPrimitiveClassSneaky

      @NotNull public @NotNull Class<?> getPrimitiveClassSneaky(@NotNull @NotNull String type) throws NullPointerException
      Return the Virtual Machine's Class object for the named primitive type. The result class is equivalent to <BoxedPrimitiveType>.TYPE. This method is similar to getPrimitiveClass(String), but it throws RuntimeException instead of ClassNotFoundException when could not find the class.

      Remember: This is forbidden magic.

      戻り値:
      primitive class
      例外:
      RuntimeException - when class was not found by specified type.
      NullPointerException - when null was provided to the type.
